Quarterly Reports.—The Committee directs the Secretary to sub-
mit a unified quarterly report detailing staffing levels and obli-
gated balances across the Department. Staffing data should provide
detail by agency, including current levels and end-of-year goals,
and the source of appropriations, notated by the authority citation,
supporting each staffing level. Obligation data should include year-
to-date obligations and current balances at the mission area, agen-
