a revenue alfalfa crop insurance policy to ensure producers have a
safety net they need to produce alfalfa; the Committee directs
NASS to enhance price discovery across the country for this impor-
tant crop. Additionally, the Committee directs NASS to include the
Southeast in its crop production reporting.
Farm Labor Survey.—The Committee recognizes that recent
