Laying Hen and Turkey Research.—The Committee notes that re-
search into laying hens and turkeys holds the potential to improve
the efficiency and sustainability of laying hen and turkey produc-
tion through integrated collaborative research and technology
transfer. The Committee provides funding to support research into
laying hen and turkey disease prevention, antimicrobial resistance,
nutrition, gut health, and alternative housing systems under ex-
treme weather conditions. The Committee encourages NIFA to im-
